Package com.biokey.client.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalysisEngineService
    Service that runs the analysis model and reports analysis results that represent the likelihood that the user's typing matches their current profile.
    ChallengeService
    Service that responds to changes in client status and locks or unlocks the OS accordingly.
    ClientInitService
    Service that retrieves the client state from the disk and OS and ensures that it has not been corrupted.
    ClientInitServiceIntegrationTest  
    KeyloggerDaemonService
    Service that records user key strokes in the background and registers them to the client state.
    ServerListenerService
    Service that listens for messages enqueued by the server and responds by registering the changes to the client state.
